data.description: Calling all investors and savvy buyers ready to renovate this lovely semi-detached home in Brightwood.  The home is in need of a complete renovation but has great bones and a great floor plan. The home currently features 3 levels, 3 bedrooms,  and 2.2 bathrooms, there is only a toilet in basement.  The main level floor plan is already very open and offers, living room, dining room and kitchen. The top level features 3 bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms including a front facing master suite. The basement level is prepared with space for an additional bedroom or rec room, wash/dryer hookup, bathroom  and rear exist. The home also features offset parking front and rear year, and a covered porch.   The home will only be shown via open house. Bring all offers.
